body:
Version with two returns makes difference.
Here are the measurements on the trivial code from the top.

Before:
````
real 0m14.468s
user 0m12.504s
sys  0m1.812s
````

With both returns:
````
real 0m2.412s
user 0m2.006s
sys  0m0.479s
````

After removing first return:
````
real 0m14.240s
user 0m12.397s
sys  0m1.614s
````
